{"tid":2257750,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"一個完美嘅魚香茄子煲真係可遇不可求","createTime":"2020-10-25T12:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T14:26:30.000Z","uid":166054,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a4455fe9c6d778ae6a5fe35e4bbdb2f15fe6bd0","tid":2257750,"uid":166054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺食魚香茄子煲通常唔會中伏<br />\n但食到一個完美嘅魚香茄子煲真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最普遍嘅問題係煲嘢太多油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愈食愈漏（潷潷下變咗油撈飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n第二個問題通常係冇乜鹹香，食中粒鹹魚就正，除此之外食落去會嫌佢唔夠惹味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個食過沙田禾輋邨嘅康樂飯店，佢係我咁耐以嚟唯一食過真係覺得完美嘅魚香茄子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以上嘅缺點都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飯都食多幾碗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜之後康樂執咗（多謝領匯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）到而家我都重揾緊一道魚香茄子可以食返佢個味道，但重未遇得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講咗咁耐，都係求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但藍店不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ea7b8b7fe3df210a5ddad166bbfb271b49aa0d","tid":2257750,"uid":381575,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:41:25.000Z","msg":"粉紅色lin頭，可遇不可求"},{"pid":"9e7765fee70b6372f9c5ab90ee31954b795af73d","tid":2257750,"uid":166054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28ea7b8b7fe3df210a5ddad166bbfb271b49aa0d","tid":2257750,"uid":381575,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:41:25.000Z","msg":"粉紅色lin頭，可遇不可求"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"一樣咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af204bc06b0af034cfad1d965d0bd48954bfade7","tid":2257750,"uid":299187,"like"