":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f57cd31f8903b2d40cc63193e2f5ca53741f4d90","tid":2257750,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"根本上魚香茄子，就唔應該走油嘅， 啲油封實咗 茄子一啲都唔入味"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:41:10.000Z","msg":"識野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食親啲茄子keep返一枝枝喺度嘅都冇泥味道<br />\n煮爛佢餸飯先係一流"},{"pid":"69b65f806318e53fbb578dcfc024bdb594e0431c","tid":2257750,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f57cd31f8903b2d40cc63193e2f5ca53741f4d90","tid":2257750,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"根本上魚香茄子，就唔應該走油嘅， 啲油封實咗 茄子一啲都唔入味"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"咪玩，傳統煮法一定係走油<br />\n你有咩新方法咪提出，講咩唔應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948a222044afa1bb689ed4a991a2d5c8d80c57ac","tid":2257750,"uid":299187,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e1035cea1606bbc254c7251ae3cb22a3c83f0f25","tid":2257750,"uid":166054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59a66581ff5399e022198b9d2a2f5e84a51147e4","tid":2257750,"uid":299187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af204bc06b0af034cfad1d965d0bd48954bfade7","tid":2257750,"uid":299187,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:48:10.000Z","msg":"李錦記包醬好食過好多大牌檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"自己再加返D新鮮蒜、乾蔥同辣椒<br />\n屌打好多餐廳<br />\n橫掂你出街食都有味精<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T12:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />配埋茄子同煲就係魚香茄子煲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:59:15.000Z","msg":"茄子2條、豬肉碎（用少少生抽同生粉加D水醃下，唔醃都得），咸魚我無加，咁少唔知點買<br />\n落油爆香蒜乾蔥辣椒，煎香豬肉碎，加醬爆香，（呢度我會加2、3湯匙水/雞湯，隨心，唔加都得）再加茄子炒，焗到淋身，生粉水睇下有無需要先加<br />\n試下啦幾蚊包，街市雜貨鋪同超市都好易搵到<br />\n試過幾個KOL嘅食譜，都係包醬好食D<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋餐廳D煲仔都係喺個鑊炒，燒熱隻煲上菜，好似上鐵板咁，因為熱同香，覺得好食好多"},{"pid":"1f3aa082d8f3f05dba95fb53e566c8da50f25249","tid":2257750,"uid":299187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69b65f806318e53fbb578dcfc024bdb594e0431c","tid":2257750,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f57cd31f8903b2d40cc63193e2f5ca53741f4d90","tid":2257750,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"根本上魚香茄子，就唔應該走油嘅， 啲油封實咗 茄子一啲都唔入味"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"咪玩，傳統煮法一定係走油<br />\n你有咩新方法咪提出，講咩唔應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:04:03.000Z","msg":"個人喜好<br />\n屋企煮試過蒸/ 走油/ 直接炒<br />\n蒸完好多水，走油好Q油，茄子本身成舊海綿咁吸哂D油<br />\n最後我直接炒再焗到佢軟身都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffc3411bc9b5016876d9860119c4d6ed019d0e9","tid":2257750,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f3aa082d8f3f05dba95fb53e566c8da50f25249","tid":2257750,"uid":299187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69b65f806318e53fbb578dcfc024bdb594e0431c","tid":2257750,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f57cd31f8903b2d40cc63193e2f5ca53741f4d90","tid":2257750,"uid":44454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:35:47.000Z","msg":"根本上魚香茄子，就唔應該走油嘅， 啲油封實咗 茄子一啲都唔入味"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T13:51:35.000Z","msg":"咪玩，傳統煮法一定係走油<br />\n你有咩新方法咪提出，講咩唔應該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:04:03.000Z","msg":"個人喜好<br />\n屋企煮試過蒸/ 走油/ 直接炒<br />\n蒸完好多水，走油好Q油，茄子本身成舊海綿咁吸哂D油<br />\n最後我直接炒再焗到佢軟身都好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T14:05:13.00